ange report to group -5163901258:\\n\\nFormat:\\n🟡 Orbis-DTLX — 5p Update | {HH:MM} UTC {DD MMM}\\n\\nChanges detected:\\n• [list of actual changes]\\n\\nPipeline: {HEALTHY if no failures / DEGRADED if failures}\\n• Active sessions: N\\n• MCP: stitch ✅ confluence ✅ gitlab ✅\\n\\nOnly send when something changed. Stay silent when stable.\\nCurrent time: Wednesday, April 15th, 2026 - 4:54 AM (UTC) / 2026-04-15 04:54 UTC\\n\\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself.\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"timestamp\": 1776228869340,\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"86800a1c\",\n            \"seq\": 1\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"role\": \"assistant\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"thinking\",\n              \"thinking\": \"I need to check sessions_list and compare against memory/heartbeat-state.json to detect changes.\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n              \"id\": \"call_function_jclarngap20o_1\",\n              \"name\": \"sessions_list\",\n              \"arguments\": {\n                \"kinds\": [\n                  \"subagent\",\n                  \"acp\"\n                ],\n                \"messageLimit\": 3\n              }\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n              \"id\": \"call_function_jclarngap20o_2\",\n              \"name\": \"memory_search\",\n              \"arguments\": {\n                \"query\": \"heartbeat state DTLX QLHV session tracking\",\n                \"corpus\": \"memory\"\n              }\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"ahvholding\",\n          \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 430,\n            