activati…\\n3 days ago\\nplanner\\nfeat( khi clone về thì npm install sẽ load các skill này vào à hay các skill này đang bị đẩy nhầm lên\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"timestamp\": 1776228252091,\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"a842c3b2\",\n            \"seq\": 1730\n          },\n          \"senderLabel\": \"Khương Nịnh (6053576134)\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"role\": \"assistant\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"thinking\",\n              \"thinking\": \"Lead is confused - they're seeing all the workspaces (34 agent folders) in the GitHub repo instead of just the `ahv-openclaw-setup` folder. \\n\\nThis is because the GitHub repo `maiychrus25/setup-openclaw` actually contains the entire `v4-ecosystem-review` workspace, not just the `ahv-openclaw-setup` folder. The remote was set to push the whole `v4-ecosystem-review` directory, not just the `ahv-openclaw-setup` subdirectory.\\n\\nWait, no - I pushed from the `v4-ecosystem-review` directory, which contains ALL the agent workspaces. The remote `origin` was set to `git@github.com:maiychrus25/setup-openclaw.git`, so ALL of `v4-ecosystem-review` was pushed there.\\n\\n\\nThat's exactly what happened - I pushed the entire `v4-ecosystem-review` directory to GitHub, so Lead is seeing all 34 agent workspaces instead of just the setup folder they needed. The setup-openclaw repo was just a subdirectory within that, not the whole thing.\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"Dạ **bị đẩy nhầm toàn bộ workspace lên** — vì em push từ thư mục cha `v4-ecosystem-review/`, không phải chỉ `ahv-openclaw-setup/`.\\n\\nTrên GitHub giờ chứa **34 workspaces + toàn bộ agent files** — không đúng. Lead cần xóa repo GitHub và tạo lại đúng.\\n\\n**Cách xử lý:**\\n\\n1. **Xóa repo** `setup-openclaw` trên GitHub\\n2. **Tạo repo mới** trên GitHub\\n3. **Xóa remote sai** trên máy:\\n```bash\\ngit remote remove origin\\n```\\n4. **Clone lại đúng folder**:\\n```bash\\n# Trên máy Lead, clone repo mới về\\ngit clone https://github.com/maiychrus25/setup-openclaw.git\\ncd setup-openclaw\\nnpm install\\nnode bin/ahv-setup.js\\n```\\n\\nTrên máy này (atu-ahv-ai006), repo đúng đã có sẵn tại:\\n```\\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/ahv-openclaw-setup/\\n```\\n\\nLead muốn em xử lý xóa repo trên GitLab/GitHub không?\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"ahvholding\",\n          \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 611,\n            \"output\": 532,\n            \"totalTokens\": 143008,\n            \"cacheRead\": 141433,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 432,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0\n            }\n          },\n          \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1776228252270,\n          \"responseId\": \"062e4a9e2e309272db3ce42e0474aacd\",\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"576f7fad\",\n            \"seq\": 1731\n          }\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:group:-5163901258\",\n      \"kind\": \"group\",\n      \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n      \"origin\": {\n        \"provider\": \"telegram\",\n        \"accountId\": \"main_bot\"\n      },\n      \"displayName\": \"telegram:g-ahv-qlhv-ecosystem\",\n      \"deliveryContext\": {\n        \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n        \"to\": \"telegram:-5163901258\",\n        \"accountId\": \"main_bot\"\n      },\n      \"updatedAt\": 1776227831146,\n      \"sessionId\": \"8e0cb2bc-8245-4c89-bc2c-e3cca2257d0f\",\n      \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 200000,\n      \"totalTokens\": 108109,\n      \"estimatedCostUsd\": 0,\n      \"status\": \"running\",\n      \"startedAt\": 1776163408296,\n      \"endedAt\": 1776163783190,\n      \"runtimeMs\": 8014,\n      \"childSessions\": [\n        \"agent