ture is done (34 agents, presence system, etc.), but there are some cleanup items:\n\n\n- Need to push the 17 commits to origin/main\n- The project repos sitting in the v4-ecosystem-review workspace should probably live elsewhere\n- ops-manager cleanup is partially done\n- The `ahv-openclaw-setup` package looks like the actual migration script\n\nI should clarify with the user what specific migration plan they're referring to, since the v4 infrastructure itself is complete."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_5db3uvt21i7b_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review && git log origin/main..HEAD --oneline | head -20"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":351,"output":278,"totalTokens":23493,"cacheRead":21721,"cacheWrite":1143,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776226544532,"responseId":"062e43f1811a478cf13f9fe7f0c373a5","__openclaw":{"id":"02da540b","seq":10}},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a full picture. Let me summarize for the Lead:\n\n**V4 Ecosystem Migration - Status:**\n\n✅ **Infrastructure (DONE):**\n- 34 agent workspaces created\n- Presence system (init/set/broadcast)\n- SKILL_GATES.md for all 34 agents\n- DEV_GATE.md for 5 key agents\n- HANDOVER.md / FEEDBACK.md templates\n- OPENSPEC_TRIGGER\n- Ecosystem backup (2026-04-11)\n- GIT_WORKFLOW.md (ecosystem standard)\n- 17 commits ahead of origin/main (NEED PUSH)\n\n⚠️ **Pending Cleanup:**\n\n\n- Project repos sitting in the v4-ecosystem-review workspace that should be relocated\n- ops-manager directory partially cleaned up with remaining deleted files\n- ahv-openclaw-setup package needs review for how it fits into the migration\n\nI should clarify with the Lead what they mean by \"plan migration\" — whether they're asking about the v4 infrastructure setup status or something else entirely."},{"type":"text","text":"## V4 Ecosystem Migration — Status\n\n**Tổng quan:**\n\n| Hạng mục | Trạng thái |\n|---|---|\n| 34 agent workspaces | ✅ Hoàn tất |\n| Presence system | ✅ Hoàn tất |\n| SKILL_GATES / DEV_GATE | ✅ Hoàn tất |\n| HANDOVER / FEEDBACK templates | ✅ Hoàn tất |\n| Ecosystem backup | ✅ (2026-04-11) |\n| GIT_WORKFLOW.md | ✅ Hoàn tất |\n| **17 commits chưa push** | ⚠️ Cần push lên origin/main |\n\n**Chưa xong / Cần dọn dẹp:**\n- Project repos (`ahv-qlhv-be`, `ahv-qlhv-fe`, `ahv-dtlx-backend`) nằm trong workspace v4-ecosystem-review — không đúng chỗ\n- `ahv-openclaw-setup` — cần review xem có phải migration script chính thức không\n- ops-manager: đã xóa nhưng chưa commit cleanup\n\n**Cần Lead xác nhận:** \"Plan migration\" ở đây là migration gì?\n1. **V4 infrastructure** → ✅ gần xong, cần push 17 commits + dọn repo\n2. **Migration script (ahv-openclaw-setup)** → đọc nội dung rồi báo cáo\n3. **Khác** → nói rõ hơn\n\nChờ Lead hướng dẫn tiếp."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":477,"output":565,"totalTokens":24430,"cacheRead":22455,"cacheWrite":933,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776226552335,"responseId":"062e43f9b5eb94d8ca5013359b1987c9","__openclaw":{"id":"6d34c150","seq":12}}]},{"key":"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:e7885813-0446-4101-a171-941c2416848e","kind":"other","channel":"webchat","label":"Cron: Agent Status to Lead","displayName":"webchat:g-agent-master-orchestrator-cron-e7885813-0446-4101-a171-941c2416848e","deliveryContext":{"channel":"webchat"},"updatedAt":1776226484570,"sessionId":"1809bef8-e85f-45f1-bec9-a828745f9877","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":34262,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"running","startedAt":1776226484036,"systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"webchat","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/1809bef8-e85f-45f1-bec9-a828745f9877.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I hav